ets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900621a3988dd334924b136a73176297a2d52399","tid":496353,"uid":64990,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T15:48:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你地訓咁少 個人會運作到架咩<br />\n我諗野 記野 會變得好慢<br />\n所以寧願訓多啲 玩少啲 一起身就溫溫溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   當你人生畀返工霸佔左接近 40%以上既 時間, 你仲會唔會咁諗呀 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當返工都返十幾粒鐘既時間，返到屋企就算訓少幾粒鐘，都會抽啲時間出黎做自己野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}